    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J179">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If I could bribe them by a Rose</l>
                    <l>I'd bring them every flower that grows</l>
                    <l>From Amherst to Cashmere!</l>
                    <l>I would not stop for night, or storm --</l>
                    <l>Or frost, or death, or anyone --</l>
                    <l>My business were so dear!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If they w'd linger for a Bird</l>
                    <l>My Tamborin were soonest heard</l>
                    <l>Among the April Woods!</l>
                    <l>Unwearied, all the summer long,</l>
                    <l>Only to break in wilder song</l>
                    <l>When Winter shook the boughs!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>What if they hear me! Who shall say</l>
                    <l>That such an importunity</l>
                    <l>May not at last avail?</l>
                    <l>That, weary of this Beggar's face --</l>
                    <l>They may not finally say, Yes --</l>
                    <l>To drive her from the Hall?</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
